text: Wiggler may refer to: *Wiggler (Mario), the caterpillar-like creature in the Mario series of games *Wiggler (JTAG), a parallel port JTAG tool from the Macraigor Systems LLC *Wiggler (synchrotron), an insertion device for a synchrotron *Wiggler (tool), a centering tool in metalworking *Mosquito larva, or wiggler ==See also== *Wiggle (disambiguation) *Wriggler (disambiguation)
title: Wiggler
